oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Memorial Weekend Celebration
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gaines, Earl; Curry, Clifford; Shelton, Roscoe, 1931-; Metal photoplates; Split fountain printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on split fountain, green to yellow to red) announcing Memorial Weekend Celebration featuring a Disco Friday Night on May 24, The Excello Legends : Earl Gaines, Clifford Curry, and Roscoe Shelton on May 25, and a Fashion Show on May 26 in Murfreesboro, Tennessee. Poster features metal photoplates of Earl Gaines, Clifford Curry, and Roscoe Shelton.
